title: Renewal by Type
description:
Renewal's opportunity is broken up into upcoming renewals and contracts that have already expired.

Renewal Total Actionable Opportunity Rules:

Renewals - Service value of contracts with a service line end date in the current quarter and 15 future quarters that are not past LDoS or approaching LDoS in the next 12 months.

Expired to Covered - Service value of all contracts with an expired status that expired in the curent fiscal month or the past 15 fiscal months (total of 16 months) that are not past LDoS or approaching LDoS in the next 12 months. Price basis: Historical NET Price.

title: Renewal by Period
description: Renewal's Total actionable opportunity in dollars broken up by Fiscal Quarter.

title: Renewal by
description:
Sales Level - Renewal's opportunity for each sales level according to the sales hierarchy.

Partner - Renewal's opportunity for the top 100 Partners.

Customer - Renewal's opportunity for the top Sales Account View (SAV) names.
